    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Sponge or foam-backed fabric materials, usually cut in the shape of a square or rectangle and mounted on a handle, designed to apply paint to a surface. Once dipped in paint, these tools can be used like paint brushes to evenly coat surfaces through rapid wiping motions.    </Note_Text>
